  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17">
<l>pāṅkuṇar vaiyuṟa virantukuṟai yuṟutalu</l>
<l>māṅkavaṉ viṉātalu matiyuṭa ṉākkalun</l>
<l>tuṇitaluñ cēṭpaṭa niṟuttaluñ cuṭṭiya</l>
<l>taṟiyē ṉaṟivaṉ maṟaiyē leṉṟaluṅ</l>
<l>kuṟiyā kūṟalum paṭaittaṉa moḻitalu</l>
<l>mariyā ḷeṉṟalu nīkū ṟeṉṟalu</l>
<l>nakaikoṇ ṭāṟṟalu nakāturai yeṉṟalum</l>
<l>periyīr yāmataṟ kiyaiyē meṉṟaluṅ</l>
<l>kaiyuṟai yeḷimai kāṭṭalu meyyuṟa</l>
<l>ovvā teṉṟalu mavaṇilai yuṇarntu</l>
<l>koḷkuva ṉeṉṟalu maṭaṉmā kūṟalu</l>
<l>maṟṟatu vilakkaluṅ kaiyuṟai kōṭalum</l>
<l>viḻaiya vuṇarttalu nāṇoṭu nīṅkalum</l>
<l>valitākac collik kuṟainayap pittalun</l>
<l>taḻīik kōṭalun taḻaiyēṟ pittaluṅ</l>
<l>kaiyuṟai yetirntamai meypeṟa vicaittalum</l>
<l>virumpiṭa muraittaluṅ kuṟiyoṭu nīṅkalum</l>
<l>puṉaintu nilaiyalu nilaimai kūṟalum</l>
<l>pāṅkikoṇ ṭikattalum pakaṟkuṟi yākum.</l>
</lg></div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV17comm1">e-tu. tōḻiyiṟ kūṭṭattup pakaṟ kuṟi yām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The quoted [<hi rend="italic">cūttiram</hi>] intends to make known the way 
      in which the daytime meeting-place occurs.</p>
      <p xml:id="TNV17comm2">pāṅkiyai yuṇarntatu mutalākak koṇṭu peyarnta tīṟākac collap paṭṭaṉa 
      vellān tōḻiyiṉ ākiya pakaṟ kuṟik kūṭṭam ām eṉṟa vāṟu.</p> 
<p xml:lang="en">All of the things mentioned, beginning with 'making known [his desire] to the <hi rend="italic">tōḻi</hi>' 
and ending with '[the <hi rend="italic">tōḻi</hi>] taking [the heroine] and departing', are the union at the daytime meeting-place 
on account of the <hi rend="italic">tōḻi</hi>.</p>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem1">
      <l>nōkkiṉum piṟamuka nōkkāḷ cāriṉum</l>
<l>pūkkuḻaṉ maṭantai tōḷcā rummē</l>
<l>yaṉṉa talaiyaḷi yuṭaimaiyi</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉuyirt tōḻiyiv vēntiḻai yivaṭkē</l></lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu1">eṉpatu pāṅkiyai yuṇarntatu.</p></div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem2">
<l>puṉaiyiḻai yāyamoṭu pūmpan teṟiyavu</l>
<l>naṉaimalar ñāḻa loḷvī koyyavum</l>
<l>varuntiṉaḷ kollō maṭantai</l>
<l>parantaṉṟu mātō paṇpukeḻu niṟaṉē</l></lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu2">eṉpatu vēṟu pāṭu kaṇṭu pāṅki yaiyuṟṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem3">
<l>kaṇṇi takaiciṟan taṉavē taṇṇeṉ</l>
<l>pūntaḻai cevviya pōlum vāṅkiruṅ</l>
<l>kūntalu malkulum poliya</l>
<l>vēntiṉir koṇmiṉyām viḻaikuvam peritē</l></lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu3">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ irantu kuṟai yuṟṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem4">
<l>vaikal vaika laiya vivvaḻik</l>
<l>kaiyuṟai yēntiṉir varutir maṟṟaḵ</l>
<l>taṟikalam yāmemark kuraippiṟ</l>
<l>peṟukuvi rentai peruvaṇ maiyaṉē</l></lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu4">eṉpatu talaimakaṉait tōḻi viṉāyiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem5">
<l>ampumukaṅ kiḻitta vempuṇ vāya</l>
<l>kalaimāṉ pōntaṉa vuḷavōnum</l>
<l>maṭamā ṉōkka marīiṉa paṭarntē</l></lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu5">eṉpatu kavarntu niṉṟa tōḻiyai mati yuṭaṉ paṭuppāṉ uṟṟut tōḻiyun 
talaimakaḷum uṭaṉ āya vaḻit talaimakaṉ viṉāyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV17poem6">
<l>uraimi ṉīrma ṉemakkē varaiyiṭai</l>
<l>yarumpaṭark kavalai nīnti</l>
<l>peruntuya raruppam peyartaru neṟiyē</l>
</lg></div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu6">eṉpatu vaḻi viṉāyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV17poem7"> 
        <l>kaiyatu ceyalaiyan taḻaiyē viṉāya</l>
        <l>teypuṇ vāya māvē kaiviṭ</l>
        <l>ṭakalā ṉammaviv vakaṉpuṉan</l>
        <l>takaiyō ṉuḷḷiya taṟiyalam peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
<p xml:id="TNV17koḷu7">eṉpatu talaimakaṉait tōḻi yaiyuṟṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
